hadiths[158]{hadithnumber,text}:
679,"Ibrahim ne Aswad se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham (beeviyan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) mein se kisi aik ke khususi dinon mein hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chadar baandhney ka hukm detey, wo chadar baandh leti to phir aap uske sath let jatey."
680,"Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham mein se kisi ke khususi din hotey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske josh aur kasarat ke dinon mein usey tehband baandhney ka hukm detey, phir uske sath let jatey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : tum mein se kon hai jo apni khahish par is qadr zabt rakhta ho jis qadr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni khahish par qaabu rakhtey they."
681,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ke khas dinon mein kapdey ke uper unke sath lag kar let jatey."
682,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad kiye huey ghulam abu-Kuraib ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se suna, kaha : jab mere makhsoos dinon hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere sath let jatey (us waqt) mere aur aap ke darmyan kapda beech mein hota tha."
683,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath roein-daar chadar mein leti hui thi, is beech mein mere dinon ka shuruat ho gaya aur main khisak gaee aur un dinon ke kapdey ley liye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : kya tumharey din shuru ho gaey? maine jawab diya : ji haan. to aap ne mujhey paas bula liya aur main aap ke sath odhney ki aik hi roein daar chadar mein let gaee. Umme-Salma ne bataya ke wo aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ikatthey aik bartan mein ghusle-janabat kar letey they."
684,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Umra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf kartey to apna sar (ghar ke darwazey se) mere qareeb kar detey, main usmein kanghi kar deti aur aap insani zarurat ke baghair ghar mein tashrif na latey they."
685,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne Leis se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa aur Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : (jab mein aetikaf mein hoti to) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye ghar mein dakhil hoti, usmein koi bimar hota to main bas guzartey-guzartey hi us se (haal) poochh leti aur agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid se mere paas ( hujrey mein) sar dakhil farmatey to main usmein kanghi kar deti, jab aap aetikaf mein hotey to ghar mein kisi (haqeeqii) zarurat ke baghair dakhil na hotey. ibne-Rumeh ne (jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) motakif hotey, ke bajaaey), jab sab log aetikaf mein hotey, kahaa."
686,"Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Nofal ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haalat aetikaf mein masjid se meri taraf sar nikaaltey to main khususi dinon mein hotey huey usko dho deti."
687,Hisham ne kaha : Urwa ne hamein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (aitikaaf ki haalat mein) apna sar mere qareeb kar detey jabke main apne hujrey mein hoti aur main haiz ki haalat mein aap ke sar mein kanghi kar deti thi.
688,"Aswad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main khas dinon main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar dho deti thi."
689,"Aamash ne Saabit-bin-Ubaid se, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mujhey masjid mein se jaey Namaz pakda do. kaha : maine kaha : main haaiza hun. aap ne farmaya : tumhara haiz tumharey hath mein nahi hai."
690,"Hajjaj aur ibne-abi-Ghaniya ne Sabit se, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main masjid se aapko jaey Namaz pakda dun, maine kaha : main haaiza hun. aap ne farmaya : haiz tumharey hath mein nahi hai."
691,"saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein they. itney mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Aaisha ! mujh ko kapda utha de'' unhon-ne kaha : main haaiza hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tera haiz terey hath mein nahi hai'' phir unhon-ne kapda utha diya."
692,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Misar aur Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Miqdaam-bin-Shureh se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main khas dinon ke doran mein pani pi kar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pakda deti to aap apna munh mere munh ki jagah par rakh kar pani pi letey, aur main daanton ke sath haddi se gosht nochti jabke mere makhsoos din hotey, phir wo ( haddi ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko deti to aap mere munh wali jagah par apna munh rakhtey (aur buti todtey.) Zuhair ne ( فیشرب ( ) pani peeney (ka lafz zikr nahi kya."
693,Safiya-binte-Sheba ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main haiz ki haalat mein hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri god ko takiya banatey aur Quran padhtey .
694,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke yahoodi, jab unki koi aurat haaiza hoti to na wo uske sath khana khaatey aur na uske sath ghar hi mein ikatthey rehtey. chunanche Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne aap se us barey mein poochha, is par Allah Taala ne aayat utari : ye aap se haiz ke barey mein sawal kartey hain, aap farma dijiye , ye azeeyat (ka waqt) hai, isliye maheez ( maqam haiz ( mein aurton (ke sath ham-bistari) se door ho, aakhir tak. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hambistari ke siwa sab kuchh karo. yahudiyon tak ye baat pahunchi to kehney lagey : ye aadmi hamarey Deen ki har baat ki mukhalifat hi karna chahta hai. (ye sun kar) Usaid-bin-Huzair aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur donon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! yahood is-is tarah kehtey hain to kya ham un (aurton ( se hambistari bhi na kar liya karein? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya yahan tak ke ham ne samjha ke aap donon se naraz ho gaey hain. wo donon nikal gaey, aagey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye doodh ka hadiya aa raha tha, aap ne kisi ko unke peechhey bheja aur unko ( bulwaakar ( doodh pilaya, wo samajh gaey ke aap unse naraz nahi huey."
695,"Wakee, abu-Muawiya aur Hushaim ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne munzir bin Yala se ( jinki kunniyat abu Yala hai) unhon-ne ibn-Hanfiya se, unhon-ne (apne walid (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey mazi (mani se mukhtalif ratoobat jo usi rastey se khaarij hoti hai) zyada aati thi aur main aap ki beti ke (saath) rishtey ki wjah se seedhey-seedhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochhney mein sharm mehsus karta tha. maine Miqdaad-bin-Aswad se kaha, unhon-ne aap se poochha, aap ne farmaya : (is mein mubtlaa aadmi ( khas uzu (ang) ko dhoey aur wuzu kar ley."
696,"Shoba ne Sulaiman Aamash se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (ke sath rishtey ( ki wjah se Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mazi ke barey mein poochhney mein sharm mehsus ki to maine Miqdad ko kaha, unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, aap ne farmaya is se wuzu ( karna padta ( hai."
697,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat hai, kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham ne Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja , unhon-ne aap se mazi ke barey mein puchha jo insan (ke khas uzu (khaas ang)) se khaarij hoti hai ke wo uska kya karey? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wuzu karo aur sharm gaah ko dho lo. (tarteeb mein pahley dhonaa, phir wuzu karna hai jis tarah hadis : 695 mein hai.)"
698,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko uthey, qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki, phir apna chehra aur donon hath dhoey , phir so gaey."
699,abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab janabat ki haalat mein sona chahtey to soney se pahley Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu kar letey they.
700,"ibne-Ulaih, Wakee aur ghandar ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Hakam se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki : unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab haalate-janabat mein hotey aur khana ya sona chahtey to Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu kar letey they."
701,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashaar donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai, isi tarah Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne hadis sunai. un donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis sunai. ibne- Musanna ki hadis mein hai, Hakam ne kaha : maine Ibrahim ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna. ( aagey wahi hadis hai jo uper bayan hui. ("
702,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham mein se koi janabat ki haalat mein ho to kya wo (usi tarah) so sakta hai? aap ne farmaya : haan , jab wuzu kar ley."
703,"ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai (kaha : ( mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se fatwa malum kya aur kaha : kya ham mein se koi shakhs janabat ki haalat mein so sakta hai? aap ne farmaya : haan , wuzu kar ley phir (us waqt tak ke liye) so jaey jab wo ghusl karna chaahey. ,"
704,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney zikr kya ke raat ke waqt wo janabat ki halat mein ho jatey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : wuzu kar aur (is se pahley) uzu (khaas ang) dho lo, phir so jao."
705,"Leis ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qais se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke witr ke barey mein sawal kya. . . . . phir aagey hadis bayan ki ke maine puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janabat ki surat mein kya kartey they? kya soney se pahley ghusl farmatey they ya ghusl se pahley so jatey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : aap ye sab kar letey they, kabhi-kabhi naha kar sotey aur kabhi-kabhi wuzu karke so jatey. maine kaha : Allah Taala ka shukr hai jisne ( Deen ke) mamley mein wusat rakhi hai."
706,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi aur ibne- Wahab donon ne Muawiya-bin-Saleh se pichhli sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki
707,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hadis sunai, neez abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi-Zayda ne khabar di, neez Amr Naqid aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Marwan bin Muawiya fazari ne hadis sunai, un sab ( Hafs , ibne-abi-Zayda aur Marwan ( ne Aasim se, unhon-ne abu-Mutwakkil se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ne apni biwi se mubashrat kar li, phir se karna chahey to wo wuzu kar ley. ( Hafs bin Ghiyas se riwayat karne waale) Abu-Bakar ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kya : donon baar ke darmyan wuzu kar ley , neez ( أن يعود ( ) phir se) ke bajaey ( أن يعاود ( ) dobara (ke alfaz istemal kiye."
708,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi ghusl se apni (eik se zyada ( beeviyon ke paas jatey they.
709,"Ishaq bin abi Talha ne kaha ke mujhey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis sunai ke Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) jo (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida aur) Ishaq ki dadi thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aap se kehney lagein jabke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi aap ke paas maujood thin, aey Allah ke rasool! aurat bhi neend ke aalim mein isi tarah khuwab dekhti hai jis tarah mard dekhta hai, wo apne aap se wahi cheez ( nikalti hui ( dekhti hai jo mard apne hawale se dekhta hai (to wo kya karey? (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehney lagein : Umme-Sulaim ! to ne aurton ko ruswa kar diya, tera dayan hath khaak aalud ho ( unka ye kehna ke tera dayan hath khaak aalud ho, buri nahi balke achi baat thi) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se farmaya : balke tumhara dayan hath khaak aalud ho. haan Umme-Sulaim ! jab wo ye dekhey to ghusl kare."
710,"Qatada se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai ke Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne (unhein ( bataya ke unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisi aurat ke barey mein puchha jo neend mein wahi cheez dekhti hai jo mard dekhta hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab aurat ye cheez dekhey to ghusl kare. Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : main is baat par sharma gaee. ( phir (aap bolin : kya aisa bhi hota hai? Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , ( warna ( phir mushabihat (similarity) kaisey paida hoti hai? mard ka pani gaadha safaid hota hai aur aurat ka pani patlaa aur zard hota hai, un donon mein se jis (ke hissey ( ko ghalba mil jaey ya ( nai tashkeel mein) sabqat ley jaey to usi se ( bachchey ki) mushabihat (similarity) hoti hai."
711,"abu-Malik Ashjai ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us aurat ke barey mein puchha jo neend mein wahi cheez dekhti hai jo mard apni neend mein dekhta hai to aap ne farmaya : jab usko wo sura pesh aaey jo mard ko pesh aati hai to wo ghusl kare."
712,"abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Zenab binte- abi Salma se aur unhon-ne (apni walida (Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah Taala haq se haya mehsus nahi karta to kya aurat ko ehtilam ho jaey to is par ghusl hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , jab ( mani ka (pani dekhey. , Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! aurat ko bhi ehtilam hota hai? aap ne farmaya : terey donon hath khaak aalud hon, uska bachcha uske mushabeh (similar) (jaisa) kaisey ho jata hai ! (yani nutfey ki tashkeel mein donon ke maaddey ka hissa hota hai.)"
713,"Hisham ke 2 shagirdon Wakee aur Sufiyan ne pichhli sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana hadis bayan ki lekin unhon-ne ye izafa kya hai : Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke maine kaha : tu ney aurton ko ruswa kar diya. (Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) donon maujood thin, tajjub ki bina par donon ke munh se yahi baat nikli .)"
714,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) jo abu Talha ke beton ki maan hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein . . . . aagey Hisham ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kya. albatta usmein ye hai ke unhon ( Urwa ( ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine us se kaha : tujh par afsos ! kya aurat ko bhi aisa nazar aata hai?"
715,"Musafe bin-Abdullah ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : kya jab aurat ko ehtilam ho jaey aur wo pani dekhey to ghusl karey? aap ne farmaya : haan. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne us aurat se kaha : terey hath khaak aalud aur zakhmi hun. unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey kuchh na kaho , kya ( bachchey ki) mushabihat (similarity) iske ilawa kisi aur wjah se hoti hai ! jab ( nutfey ki tashkeel ke marhaley mein) iska pani mard ke pani par ghalib aa jata hai to bachcha apne mamuon ke mushabeh (similar) hota hai aur jab mard ka pani aurat ke pani par ghalib aata hai to bachcha apne chachaon ke mushabeh (similar) hota hai."
716,"abu-Toba ne, jo Rabe bin Naafe hain, ham se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Muawiya bin Salam ne hamein apne bhai Zaid se hadis sunai, kaha : unhon-ne abu-Salam se suna, kaha : mujh se abu Asma Rahbi ne bayan kya ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein ye hadis sunai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas khada tha aik Yahudi aalim ( Hibr (aap ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! aap par salam ho, maine usko itney zor se dhakka diya ke wo girtey girtey bacha . usne kaha : mujhey dhakka kyon detey ho? maine kaha : tum ya Rasulullah ! nahi keh saktey ? Yahudi ne kaha : ham to aapko usi naam se pukaartey hain jo aap ke ghar walon ne aap ka rakha hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan mera naam Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hai jo mere ghar walon ne rakha hai. Yahudi bola : main aap se poochhney aaya hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey farmaya : agar main tumhen kuchh bataunga to kya tumhen us se fayda hoga? usne kaha : main apne donon kanon se tawajjoh se sununga . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik chhadi , jo aap ke paas thi, zamin par ahista-ahista maari aur farmaya : poochho . Yahudi ne kaha : jis din zamin dusri zamin se badlegi aur aasman ( bhi) badley jaeinge to log kahan hongey ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo pul ( siraat ( se ( zara ( pahley andherey mein hongey ? us ne puchha : sabse pahley kon log guzrengey ? aap ne farmaya : fuqaraaey muhajireen . Yahudi ne puchha : jab wo jannat mein dakhil hongey to unko kya pesh kya jaeyga ? to aap ne farmaya : machhli ke jigar ka zayed hissey . usne kaha : iske baad unka khana kya hoga? aap ne farmaya : unke liye jannat mein bail zabah kya jaeyga jo iske aas-paas mein charta phirta hai. usne kaha is ( khaney ( par unka mashroob kya hoga? aap ne farmaya is ( jannat (ke salsabeel naam ke chashmey se. , usne kaha : aap ne sach kaha, phir kaha : main aap se aik cheez ke barey mein poochhney aaya hun jisey ahal zamin se mahz aik Nabi janta hai ya ek 2 aur insan . aap ne farmaya : agar maine tumhen bata diya to kya tumhen us se fayda hoga? usne kaha : main kaan laga kar sununga . usne kaha : main aap se aulad ke barey mein poochhney aaya hun. aap ne farmaya : mard ka pani safaid hota hai aur aurat ka pani zard , jab donon miltey hain aur mard ka maadda manwiya aurat ki mani par ghalib aa jata hai to Allah ke hukm se donon ke yahan betaa paida hota hai aur jab aurat ki mani mard ki mani par ghalib aa jati hai to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke hukm se donon ke yahan beti paida hoti . Yahudi ne kaha : aap ne waqei sahi farmaya aur aap yaqinan Nabi hain, phir wo palat kar chala gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ne mujh se jis cheez ke barey mein sawal kya us waqt tak mujhey usmein se kisi cheez ka kuchh ilm na tha yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne mujhey iska ilm ata kar diya.'"
717,"Yahya bin Hassan ne hamein khabar di ke hamein Muawiya bin Salam ne usi asnaad ke sath isi tarah hadis sunai, siwaey iske ke) Yahya ne) ( قائما ( ) khada tha) ke bajaey ( qaaidan ( ) betha tha) kaha aur ( زیادۃ کبد النون) ke bajaey) (زائدۃ کبدالنون) kaha (mana aik hi hai) aur unhon-ne (اذکر و آنت) (iske haan beta aur beti ki wiladat hoti hai) ke alfaz kahey , aur (اذکر و آنثا) (un donon ke yahan beta paida hua hai aur un donon ke yahan beti paida hoti hai) ke alfaz nahi kahey."
718,"abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusle-janabat farmatey to pahley apne hath dhotey , phir daain hath se baain hath par pani daal kar apni sharm gaah dhotey , phir Namaz ke wuzu ki manind (tarah) wuzu farmatey, phir pani lekar ungliyon ko baalon ki jadon mein dakhil kartey, jab aap samajhtey ke aap ne achi tarah jadon mein pani pahuncha diya hai. to apne sar par donon hathon se teen chullu daaltey. phir sarey jism par pani daltey (aur jism dhotey ( phir ( aakhir mein) apne donon paon dho letey."
719,"Jareer, Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur ibne-Numair ne Hisham ki isi sanad ke sath (ye ( hadis riwayat ki lekin un ( teenon ( ki hadis mein paon dhoney ka zikr nahi hai."
720,"Wakee ne Hisham ki isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne janabat se ghusl farmaya, shuruat kartey huey teen baar hatheliyan dhoin . . . . . phir abu-Muawiya ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, taaham (phir bhi) paon dhoney ka zikr na kya."
721,"Zayda ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat farmatey (to ( is tarah shuruat kartey ke bartan mein hath dakhil karne se pahley apne donon hath dhotey , phir Namaz ke liye apne wuzu ki tarah wuzu farmatey."
722,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne ham se hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( ham se Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Kureb se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey meri khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghusle-janabat ke liye aap ke qareeb pani rakha , aap ne apni donon hatheliyon ko do ya teen baar dhoya , phir apna (daayan) hath bartan mein dakhil kya aur uske zariey se apni sharm gaah par pani daala aur usey apne baain hath se dhoya , phir apne baaein hath ko zamin par mar kar achi tarah ragda aur apna Namaz jaisa wuzu farmaya, phir hatheli bhar kar teen lap pani apne sar par daala , phir apne sarey jism ko dhoya , phir apni us jagah se door hat gaey aur apne donon paon dhoey , phir main tauliya aap ke paas laai to aap ne usey wapas kar diya."
723,"Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ne Aamash ki pichhli sanad ke sath ye riwayat bayan ki lekin un donon ki hadis mein sar par teen lap dalney ka zikr nahi hai. Wakee ki hadis mein poorey wuzu ki kaifiyat ka bayan hai. usmein ( unhon-ne ( kulli aur naak mein pani dalney ka zikr kya, aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis mein tauliye ka zikr nahi hai."
724,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Aamash ki pichhli sanad ke sath Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki riwayat bayan ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tauliya laya gaya to aap ne usey hath na lagaya aur pani ke sath is tarah karne lagey, yani jhadney lagey."
725,"Qasim (bin Muhammad-bin abi-Bakr ( ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat farmatey to taqriban itna bada bartan mangwatey jitna ontni ka doodh dhoney ka hota hai. aur chullu pani letey aur sar ke daain hissey se shuruat farmatey, phir baain taraf (pani daltey ( , phir donon hathon (ka lap bana kar us ( se (pani) letey aur unse sar par) pani ( daaltey."
726,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi bartan se, jo aik farq ( teen saa ya saadhey 13 لٹر (ka tha, ghusle-janabat farmaya kartey they"
727,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne- Rumeh ne Leis se, isi tarah Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, un donon ( Leis aur Sufiyan ( ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik badey pyaley se, jo aik farq ki miqdar jitna tha, ghusl farmatey. main aur aap aik bartan mein (se ( ghusl kartey they. Sufiyan ki hadis main ( في الإنا ء الواحد (ke bajaey) ( من إناء waahid ( (eik bartan se) hai. Quteba ne kaha, Sufiyan ne kaha : farq teen saa ka hota hai."
728,"Abu-Bakar bin Hafs ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman (bin Auf jo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik bhaanjey they) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka dudh-sharik bhai ( Abdullah-bin Yazeed ( unki khidmat mein hazir huey to usne unse Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghusle-janabat ke barey mein sawal kya, chunanche unhon-ne aik saa ke baqdr bartan mangwaya aur us se ghusl kya, hamarey aur unke darmyan ( diwar wghaira ka ( parda rukawat tha, apne sar par teen baar pani dala. abu-Salma ne bataya ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyan apne sar (ke baalon ( ko kaat leti thin yahan tak ke wo ( وفرہ ( ) kanon ke nichley hissey ki lambai ke baal ( ki tarah ho jatey."
729,"Bukair bin-Abdullah ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl farmatey to daain hath se shuruat farmatey, is par pani daal kar usey dhotey, phir jahan na-pasandida cheez lagi hoti usey daain hath se pani daal kar baain hath se dhotey, jab us se farigh ho jatey to sar par pani daaltey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan se nahatey jabke donon janabat ki haalat mein hotey ."
730,Hafsa binte-Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr se (jo munzir bin Zuber ki ahliya thiin) riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke wo ( khud (aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan mein ghusl kartey jis mein teen mudd ( mudd aik saa ka chotha hissa hota hai) ya iske qareeb pani aata
731,"Qasim-bin-Muhammad (bin abi-Bakr ( ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, farmaya : main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan se ghusle-janabat kartey aur hamarey hath baari-baari usmein jatey"
732,"(Hazrat Aaisha ki shagird ( Muaza binte- Abdullah ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan se, jo mere aur aap ke darmyan hota, ghusl kartey. aap meri nisbat jald pani letey yahan tak ke main kehti : mere liye chhodiye , mere liye chhodiye . wo ( Muaza ( kehti hai aur wo donon junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) hotey ."
733,"Sufiyan ne Amr se, unhon-ne abu-Shasa se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha, mujhey Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke wo aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik ( hi ( bartan mein (se ( ghusl kartey they."
734,"ibne-Juraij ne Amr-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey jitna zyada (se zyada ( ilm hai aur jo mere zahan mein aata hai iske mutabiq mujhey abu-Shasa ne khabar di ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke bachey huey pani se naha letey they."
735,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke wo aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik bartan mein (se ( ghusle-janabat kartey they.
736,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne bayan kya ke unke walid ne unhein hadis sunai aur ibne- Musanna ne Abdur-Rehman , yani ibne- Mehdi se hadis bayan ki, un donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah-bin Jabr se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) panch makook se ghusl farmatey aur aik makook se wuzu farmatey. (eik makook siwa saa ke barabar hota hai.) ibne- Musanna ne ( مکاکیک ( ki jagah ( Makka ki) ( kami ke sath wahi ( lafz bola. Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah kaha aur ibne- jabr ka zikr nahi kya."
737,"Misar ne ibne- jabr se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mudd se wuzu farmatey aur aik saa se panch mudd tak (ke pani ( se ghusl kartey."
738,"Bishr ne kaha : hamein abu Rehana ne Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik saa pani se ghusle-janabat farmatey aur aik mudd pani se wuzu farma letey."
739,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ali-bin hijr ne Ismail bin-Ulaih se, unhon-ne abu Rehana se, unhon-ne Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) se ( Abu-Bakar ne kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi (Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik saa pani se ghusl farmatey aur aik mudd pani se wuzu farma letey. ( Ali ( ibne- hijr ki riwayat mein hai ke ya ( abu Rehana ne aik mudd se wuzu farma letey they ke bajaey) , aik mudd pani se aap ka wuzu ho jata tha. abu Rehana ne kaha : Safina (Raziallahu anhu) kafi umr ke ho gaey they, isliye mujhey unki hadis par aitimad aur yaqin nahi hai."
740,"abu-Ahwas ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin Surad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ghusl ke mutaalliq aik doosrey se takraar ki, chunanche kuch ne kaha : lekin main, main to sar ko itna aur itna dhota hun. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : lekin main to apne sar par teen hatheliyan bhar kar) pani ( daalta hun."
741,"Shoba ne abu Ishaq se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin Surad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ke paas ghusle-janabat ka zikr kya gaya to aap ne farmaya : lekin main, main to apne sar par teen baar pani bahata hun."
742,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Ismail bin Salim ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, unhon-ne abu Bishr se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Saqif ke wafad ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, aur kaha : hamara ilaqa aik thanda ilaqa hai to ghusl kaisey ho? aap ne farmaya : lekin main, main to apne sar par teen baar pani bahata hun. ibne- Salim ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ham se Hushaim ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha hamein abu Bishr ne bataya aur kaha : bila shubah Saqif ke wafad ne ( sawal poochhtey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mukhatab karke ( kaha : aey Allah ke rasool!"
743,"imam Jafar ke walid imam Muhammad Baaqar bin Ali-bin Husain rahma للہ ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat kartey to sar par pani ki teen lappein daltey , chunanche Hasan-bin- Muhammad ne unse kaha : mere baal to zyada hain. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to maine us se kaha : aey bhatijey ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal tumharey baalon se zyada aur umda they."
744,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Ayub bin-Musa se, unhon-ne Saeed bin abi Saeed Maqbari se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke Maula Abdullah-bin-Ubai Raafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mein aik aisi aurat hon ke kis kar sar ke baalon ki choti banati hon to kya ghusle-janabat ke liye usko kholun ? aap ne farmaya : nahi, tumhen bas itna hi kafi hai ke apne sar par teen chullu pani dalo , phir apne aap par pani baha lo tum paak ho jaogi."
745,Yazid-bin-Harun aur Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein isi sanad ke sath Sufiyan Sory ne Ayub bin-Musa ke hawale se khabar di aur Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis mein hai : kya main haiz aur janabat (ke ghusl (ke liye usko kholun ? to aap ne farmaya : nahi. aagey ibne-Uena ki hadis ke ham mana (riwaayat ( bayan ki.
746,Ayub bin-Musa se ( Sufiyan Sory ke bajaey) Rooh bin-Qasim ne usi (pichhli sanad) ke sath riwayat ki ke unhon ( Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : kya main choti ko khol kar ghusle-janabat karun? . . . . . . unhon ( Rooh bin-Qasim ( ne haiz ka tazkira nahi kya.
747,"Ubaidullah bin Umer se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye khabar pahunchi ke Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) aurton ko hukm detey hain ke wo ghusl kartey waqt sar ke baal khola karein. to unhon-ne kaha is ibne- Amr (Raziallahu anhu) par tajjub hai, aurton ko hukm deta hai ke wo jab ghusl karein to sar ke baal kholein , wo unhein ye hukm kyon nahi deta ke wo apne sar ke baal moond lein, main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi bartan se ghusl kartey they aur main us se zayed kuchh nahi karti thi ke apne sar par teen baar pani daal leti ."
748,"Amr bin-Muhammad Nafiz aur ibne-abi-Umar ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se hadis bayan ki, Amr ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Mansoor bin Safiya se, unhon-ne apni walida ( Safiya-binte-Sheba ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : wo haiz ka ghusl kaisey karey? kaha : phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke aap ne usey ghusl ka tariqa sikhaya (aur farmaya ( phir wo kastoori se ( muattar ( kapdey ka aik tukda lekar us se pakeezgi hasil kare. aurat ne kaha : main us se kaisey pakeezgi hasil karun? aap ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! us se pakeezgi hasil karo. aur aap ne ( haya se) chehra chipa liya. Sufiyan ne hamein hath ke ishaarey se munh chipa kar dikhaya . Safiya ne kaha : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : maine us aurat ko apni taraf kheench liya aur main samajh gaee thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya ( kehna ( chahtey hain to maine kaha is muattar tukdey se khoon ke nishan saaf karo. ibne-abi-Amr ne apni riwayat mein kaha : usko mil kar khoon ke nishanat par laga kar saaf karo."
749,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Mansoor ne apni walida ( Safiya-binte-Sheba ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey huey bayan kya ke aik aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke main pakeezgi (ke husool (ke liye kaisey ghusl karun? to aap ne farmaya : kastoori se muattar kapdey ka tukda lekar us se pakeezgi hasil karo. phir Sufiyan ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
750,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Ibrahim bin muhajir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Safiya se suna wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan karti thin ke Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se haiz ka ghusl ke barey mein sawal kiya? to aap ne farmaya : aik aurat apna pani aur beri ke patey lekar achi tarah pakeezgi hasil karey, phir sar par pani daal kar usko achi tarah maley yahan tak ke baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey, phir apne uper pani daaley, phir kastoori laga kapda ya rui ka tukda lekar us se pakeezgi hasil kare to Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha is se pakeezgi kaisey hasil karun? aap ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! us se pakeezgi hasil karo. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ( jaisey wo is baat ko chipa rahi hon), khoon ke nishan par laga kar. , aur us ne aap se ghusle-janabat ke barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya : (ghusl karne wali) pani lekar us se khub achi tarah wuzu karey, phir sar par pani daal kar usey maley yahan tak ke sar ke baalon ki jadon tak pahunch jaey, phir apne aap par pani daley. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Ansar ki auratein bahut khub hain, Deen ko achi tarah samajhney se sharm nahi nahin rokti."
751,"Shoba ke aik doosrey shagird Ubaidullah ke walid Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne usi (mazkura (uper zikr) (sanad se usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki aur kaha : aap ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! us se pakeezgi hasil karo, aur aap ne apna chehra chipa liya."
752,"(Shoba ke ustad) Ibrahim bin Muhajir se ( Shoba ke bajaey) abu-Ahwas ki sanad se Safiya-binte-Sheba ke hawale se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Asma binte-shakl (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! jab ham mein se koi aurat haiz ka ghusl karey to kaisey nahaey? aur (usi tarah) hadis bayan ki aur is mein ghusle-janabat ka zikr nahi kya."
753,"Wakee ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Fatima binte-abi-Hubaish (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! mein aik aisi aurat hon jisey istihaza hota hai, isliye main paak nahi ho sakti to kya main Namaz chhod dun? aap ne farmaya : nahi, ye to bas aik rag (ka khoon ( hai haiz nahi hai, lihaza jab haiz shuru ho to Namaz chhod do aur jab haiz band ho jaey to apne ( jism ( se khoon dho liya karo aur Namaz padho."
754,"Hisham ne Urwa ke (shagird Wakee ke bajaey) doosrey shagirdon abu-Muawiya , Jareer, Numer aur Hammad-bin-Zaid ki sanadon se bhi jo Wakee ki hadis ki tarah isi sanad se marwi (bayan) hai, albatta Quteba se Jarir ki riwayat ke alfaz yun hain : Fatima binte-abi-Hubaish bin abdul-Muttalib bin Asad aaein jo hamarey khandan ki aik khatun hain. Imam Muslim ne kaha : Hammad-bin-Zaid ki hadis mein aik harf zayed hai jisey ham ne zikr nahi kya"
755,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Leis se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se fatwa puchha aur kaha : mujhey istihaza hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye aik rag (ka khoon ( hai. tum ghusl karo, phir ( haiz ke dinon ke khaatmey par) Namaz padho. to wo har Namaz ke waqt ghusl karti thin. (imaam) Lais-bin-Sad ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne ye nahi kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ko har Namaz ke liye ghusl karne ka hukm diya tha. ye aisa kaam tha jo wo khud karti thin. Leis ke shagirdon mein se ibne- Rumeh ne ibna-Jahash ke alfaz istemal kiye aur Umme-Habiba nahi kaha,"
756,"( Leis ke bajaey) Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair aur Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nisbati behan ko , jo ( Ummul-Momenin Zenab bin Jahash ki behan aur) Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin, saat (7) saal tak istihaza ka aariza laahiq raha. unhon-ne iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se fatwa malum kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye haiz (ka khoon ( nahi balke ye aik rag (ka khoon ( hai, lihaza tum ghusl karo aur Namaz padho. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : wo apni behan Zenab bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke hujrey mein aik badey tasht (tab) mein ghusl kartin to pani par khoon ki surkhi ghalib aa jati. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine ye hadis Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : Allah Taala Hind par raham farmaai ! kash! wo bhi ye fatwa sun letin . Allah ki qism ! wo is baat par roti rehti thin ke istihazey ki wjah se wo Namaz nahi padh sakti thin."
757,"Ibrahim , yani ibne- Sad ne ibne-Shahab ke hawale se khabar di, unhon-ne Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein aur wo saat (7) saal tak istihazey ke aarizey mein mubtala rahen. Ibrahim bin Sad ki baqi hadis , pani par khoon ki surkhi ghalib aa jati thi, tak Amr-bin-Haris ki pichhli riwayat ki tarah hai, iske baad ka hissa unhon-ne zikr nahi kya."
758,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke binte-Jahash saat (7) saal tak istihazey mein mubtala rahin ( aagey baqi ( doosrey rawiyon ki hadis ki tarah ."
759,"Yazeed bin abi Habib ne Jafar se, unhon-ne Irak se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoon ke barey mein sawal kya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya : maine iska tab khoon se bharaa dekha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tumhen pahley jitna waqt haiz (namaz se) roktaa tha itna arsa ruki raho, phir naha lo aur Namaz padho."
760,"Ishaq ke walid Bakr bin Muzar ne Jafar bin Rabeea se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Umme-Habiba binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne, jo Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoon ( istihaza ( ki shikayat ki to aap ne unse farmaya : jitney din tumhen haiz roktaa tha itney din twaqquf karo, phir naha lo. to wo har Namaz ke liye nahaya karti thin."
761,"Hammad ne Yazeed rashk se, unhon-ne Muaza se riwayat ki ke aik aurat ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya aik aurat ayyame-haiz ki namazon ki qaza degi ? to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : kya to Harooriya ( khawaarij mein se) hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein jab ham mein se kisi ko haiz aata tha to usey ( namazon ki) qaza ka hukm nahi diya jata tha."
762,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Muaza se suna ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya : kya haaiza Namaz ki qaza de ? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : kya to harooriya ( khawaarij mein se) hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ko haiz aata tha to kya aap ne unhein ( faut shuda namazon ke) badley mein ada karne ka hukm diya ? Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : unka matlab qaza deney se tha."
763,"Aasim ne Muaza se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya, maine kaha : haaiza aurat ka ye haal kyon hai ke wo rozon ki qaza deti hai Namaz ki nahi ? unhon-ne farmaya : kya tum harooriya ho? maine kaha : main harooriya nahi, ( sirf ( poochhna chahti hun. unhon-ne farmaya : hamein bhi haiz aata tha to hamein rozon ki qaza dene ka hukm diya jata tha, Namaz ki qaza ka hukm nahi diya jata tha."
764,"abu-Nazar se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Murra ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehti thin ke main fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaee, maine aapko ghusl kartey huey paya , aap ki beti Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne aik kapdey ke zariey se aap (ke aagey ( parda banaya hua tha."
765,"Yazeed bin abi Habib ne Saeed bin abi Hind se riwayat ki ke Aqeel bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Murra ne unse hadis bayan ki ke Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke jis saal Makka fateh hua wo aap ke paas hazir huin , aap Makka ke oopri hissey mein they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nahaaney ke liye uthey to Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne aap ke aagey parda taan diya, phir (ghusl ke baad) aap ne apna kapda lekar apne gird lapeta , phir aath (8) rakatein chasht ki nafl padhein."
766,"Saeed bin abi Hind ke aik aur shagird Waleed bin Kasir ne isi sanad se hadis bayan ki aur ye alfaz kahey : to aap ki beti Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne aap ke kapdey ke zariey se aap ke liye ot bana di. aap jab ghusl kar chukey to wahi kapda liya, usey apne gird lapeta , phir khadey ho kar aath (8) rakaat Namaz ada ki, ye chasht ka waqt tha."
767,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke ghusl (ke liye pani rakha aur aapko parda muhaiya kiya to aap ne ghusl farmaya,"
768,"Zaid-bin-Hubab ne Suhak bin Usman se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin-Aslam ne khabar di, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mard, mard ka sattar na dekhey aur aurat , aurat ka sattar na dekhey. mard, mard ke sath aik kapdey mein na ho aur aurat , aurat ke sath aik kapdey mein na ho."
769,mazkura (uper zikr) riwayat ko Imam Muslim ko 2 aur ustadon Harun bin-Abdullah aur Muhammad-bin Raafe donon ne ibne-abi fidya se aur ibne-abi fidya ne usey Suhak bin Usman ki mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath bayan kya.
770,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai : kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( naql kartey huey) sunain, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kin unmein se aik ye hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Bani-Israeel be libaas ho kar, is tarah nahatey they ke aik doosrey ka sattar dekh rahe hotey aur Musa (Alaihissalam) akeley nahaya kartey they. bani-Israil kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! Musa (Alaihissalam) hamarey sath mahz isliye nahi nahatey ke unke ghadood phooley huey hain. aap ne farmaya : Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ aik baar nahaney ke liye gaey to apne kapdey aik patthar par rakh diye, patthar aap ke kapdey lekar bhag khada hua, Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ uske peechhey ye kehtey huey sarpat daud padey : O, patthar ! mere kapdey , O, patthar ! mere kapdey , yahan tak ke Bani-Israil ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sattar ko dekh liya aur kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ko to koi bimari nahi hai, jab Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ko dekh liya gaya to patthar thahar gaya, Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ne apne kapdey pahney aur patthar ko marney lagey. , Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! patthar par chh ya saat (7) nishan they, ye patthar ko Musa ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ ki mar thi."
771,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim Hanzali aur Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne Muhammad-bin-Bakr se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, neez Ishaq-bin-Mansur aur Muhammad-bin Raafe ne (aur ye alfaz un donon ke hain) Abdur-Razzaq ke hawale se ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon (ibne-Juraij) ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : jab Kaba tameer kya gaya to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) patthar dhoney lagey, Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : pattharon se hifazat ke liye apna tehband utha kar kandhey par rakh lijiye . aap ne aisa kya to aap zamin par gir gaey aur aankhen (uper ho kar) aasman par atak gain, phir aap uthey aur kaha : mera tehband, mera tehband. to aap ka tehband aapko kis kar baandh diya gaya. ibne- Raafe ki riwayat main 'apni gardan par' ke alfaz hain, unhon-ne 'apne kandhey par' nahi kaha."
772,"Zakariya-bin Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( ham se Amr-bin-Dinar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke sath Kabey ke liye patthar dho rahe they aur aap ka tehband jism par tha, us mauqe par aap ke chacha Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kaha : aey bhatijey ! behtar hoga ke tum apna tehband khol do aur usey apne mundhey par pattharon ke nichey rakh lo. Jaabir ne kaha : aap ne usey khol kar apne mundhey par rakh liya to aap ghash kha kar gir gaey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is din ke baad aapko kabhi barahna nahi dekha gaya."
773,"Hazrat Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : main aik bhari patthar uthaey huey aaya aur maine aik halka sa tehband baandha hua tha, kaha : to mera tehband khul gaya aur patthar mere paas tha. main us ( patthar ( ko nichey na rakh saka yahan tak ke usey uski jagah pahuncha diya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wapas ja kar apna kapda pahno aur nangey na chala karo."
774,"Sheban-bin-Farukh aur Abdullah-bin Muhammad-bin Asma Zubai ne kaha : hamein Mehdi bin Memun ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin abi Yaqoob ne Hasan-bin-Ali ke aazad karda ghulam Hasan-bin- Sad ke hawale se Hazrat Abdullah-bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apne peechhey sawar kar liya, phir mujhey aik raaz ki baat batai jo main kisi shakhs ko nahi bataunga , qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye aap ki mahboob tareen ot teela ya khajoor ka jhund tha. ( hadis ke aik rawi Muhammad ( ibne- Asma ne apni hadis mein kaha : ( haaish nakhl ( se murad ( haait nakhl ( khajoor ka baagh ya jhund , hai."
775,"Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed Khudri ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke main peer ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Quba gaya, jab ham banu- Salim ke mahalley mein pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ke darwazey par ruk gaey aur usey awaz di to wo apna tehband ghaseet'tey huey nikley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham ne us aadmi ko jaldi mein daal diyaa.' Utban (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap ki us mard ke barey mein kya raey hai jo biwi se jaldi hata diya jaey, halanke us ne mani khaarij na ki to usey kya karna chahiye ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pani , sirf pani se hai."
776,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : pani , bas pani se hai."
777,"abul-Ala bin Shikhkhir (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat hai, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik hadis dusri ko mansukh kar deti hai, jaisey Quran ki aik aayat dusri aayat ko mansukh kar deti hai. (yani is mafhoom ki hadisein, aap hi ke us farman ke zariey se mansukh ho chuki hain jo baad mein aayega.)"
778,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar se, unhon-ne Shoba se, unhon-ne hukm ke hawale se Zakwan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik Ansari aadmi ke) makan ke) paas se guzrey to usey bulwaya , wo us haal mein nikla ke iske sar se pani tapak raha tha to aap ne farmaya : shayad ham ne tumhen jaldi mein dala. usne kaha : ji haan, aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne farmaya : jab tumhen jaldi mein daal diya jaey ya tum inzal na kar sako to tum par ghusl lazim nahi hai, albatta wuzu zaroori hai. ibne-Bashar ne kaha : jab tumhen jaldi mein daal diya jaey ya tujhey (inzaal se) rok diya jaey."
779,"Hammad aur abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne abu Ayub se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us mard ke barey mein puchha jo apni biwi ke paas jata hai, phir usey inzal nahi hota. to aap ne farmaya : biwi se usey jo kuchh lag jaey usko dho daaley, phir wuzu karke Namaz padh ley."
780,"Shoba ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne us mard ke barey mein jo apni biwi ke paas jata hai phir usey inzal nahi hota, farmaya : wo apne uzu (khaas ang) ko dho ley aur wuzu kare."
781,"abu-Salma ne Ata-bin-Yasar se khabar di ke unhein Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ki kya raey hai, jab kisi mard ne apni biwi se mujamiat ki aur us ne mani khaarij na ki? Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( jawab mein) kaha : Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu karey aur apne uzu (khaas ang) ko dho ley. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni."
782,abu-Salma ne Ata-bin-Yasar ke bajaey Urwa-bin-Zubair se aur unhon-ne abu Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke unhon-ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi.
783,"Zuhair-bin-Harab , Abu-Ghassan Mismai , Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : ham se Muaz bin Hisham ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Qatada aur Matr ne Hasan se, unhon-ne abu Raafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab wo ( mard (us ( aurat ( ki char shakhon ke darmyan baithey, phir us se mujamiat karey to is par ghusl wajib ho jata hai. Matr ki hadis mein ye izafa hai : agarche inzal na ho. aur Imam Muslim ke asatza mein se ( sirf ( Zuhair ne ( شعبھا ( ki jagah ( أشعبها ( kaha, ( donon aik hi lafz ( شعبۃ ( ) shaakh ( ki jama hain. ("
784,Shoba ne Qatada se baqi bachi isi sanad se riwayat ki. farq ye hai ke Shoba ki is riwayat main ( ثم جهدها ( ki jagah ( ثم اجتهد ( ) phir saee ki) hai aur) w إن لم ينزل ( ) agarche inzal na ho (ke alfaz nahi hain.
785,"2 mukhtalif sanadon ke sath abu-Burda ke hawale se (unke walid (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke us masley mein muhajireen aur Ansar ke aik giroh ne ikhtilaf kya. Ansar ne kaha : ghusl sirf ( mani ke) zor se nikalney ya pani (ke inzal ( se farz hota hai aur muhajireen ne kaha : balke jab ikhtilat (milap) ho to ghusl wajib ho jata hai. ( abu-Burda ne) kaha : Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tumhen is masley se chhutkara dilata hun, main utha aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein haziri ki ijazat talab ki, mujhey ijazat de di gaee to maine kaha : meri maan , ya kaha : Ummul-Momenin ! main aap se aik cheez ke barey mein poochhna chahta hun aur mujhey aap se sharm ( bhi) aa rhi hai. to unhon-ne kaha : jo baat tum apni us maan se jisne (apne pet se) tumhen janm diya, poochh saktey they, wo mujh se poochhney mein sharm na karo kyonke main bhi tumhari maan hun. maine kaha : to kon sa ( kaam ( ghusl ko wajib karta hai? unhon-ne kaha : tum (is masley ke mutaalliq (us se miley ho jo (is se) achi tarah ba-khabar hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab wo ( mard (us ( aurat ( ki chaar shaakhon ke darmyan betha aur khatney ki jagah khatney ki jagah se mas hui to ghusl wajib ho gaya."
786,"Umme-Kulsum ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisey mard ke barey mein puchha jo apni biwi se sohbat karta hai, phir inzal nahi hota, kya un ( donon ( par ghusl hai? aur (andar (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi baithi hui thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main aur ye ( ham donon miyan biwi ( ye kartey hain, phir ham ( donon ( nahatey hain."
787,Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : aisi cheez (ke khaney ( se wuzu ( lazim ho jata ( hai jisey aag ne chhuwa ho.
788,"Abdullah-bin-Ibrahim-bin-Qariz ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko masjid mein wuzu kartey huey paya to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main to paneer ke tukdon ki bina par wuzu kar raha hun jinhein maine khaya hai kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko suna, aap farma rahe they : aisi cheez se wuzu karo jisey aag ne chhuwa ho."
789,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saeed bin Khalid-bin Amr bin Usman ne, jab main usey (pichhli sanad se) ye hadis suna raha tha, bataya ke usne Urwa-bin-Zubair se aisi cheez ( khaney ( se wuzu ke barey mein puchha jisey aag ne chhuwa hai, to Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisi cheez se wuzu karo jisey aag ne chhuwa ho."
790,"Ata-bin-Yasar ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bakri ka shana khaya, phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya."
791,"Muhammad-bin Amr bin Ata aur Ali-bin Abdullah-bin-Abbas ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gosht wali haddi ya kuchh gosht khaya, phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya ya pani ko nahi chhuwa."
792,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne kaha : hamein Zohri ne Jafar bin-Amr bin Umayya zamri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik shaney se ( gosht ( kaat kar khaatey huey dekha, phir aap ne Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya."
793,"ibne-Shahab Zohri ke doosrey shagird Amr-bin-Haris ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Amr bin Umayya se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bakri ke aik shaaney se ( gosht ( kat-tey huey dekha, phir aap ne usmein se khaya , phir aapko Namaz ki taraf bulaya gaya to aap khadey huey aur chhuri phenk di, aap ne Namaz padhi aur wuzu nahi kya."
794,ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Ali-bin Abdullah-bin-Abbas ne apne walid (Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki hai.
795,"Bukair-bin-Ashajj ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Kureb se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke yahan shaaney ka gosht khaya , phir Namaz padhi aur wuzu na kya."
796,"Yaqoob bin ashajj ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se yahi hadis bayan ki hai."
797,"Hazrat abu Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bakri ke pet (ka gosht , jigar , gurdey wghaira) bhoonta tha (aap usey khaatey ( , iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur wuzu na kartey they."
798,"Aqeel ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh nosh farmaya : phir pani talab kya, kulli ki aur farmaya : yaqinan usmein kuchh chiknaahat hai."
799,"Amr, Auzai aur Yunus sab ne Aqeel wali sanad ke sath Zohri se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
800,"Muhammad-bin Amr bin Halhala ne Muhammad-bin Amr bin Ata se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne kapdey zeb tan farmaai , phir Namaz ke liye nikley to aapko roti aur gosht ka tohfa pesh kya gaya, aap ne teen luqmey tanaawul farmaai , phir logon ko Namaz padhai aur pani ko nahi chhuwa ."
801,"Imam Muslim ne aik dusri sanad se Waleed bin Kasir ke waastey se Muhammad-bin Amr bin Ata se riwayat ki, kaha : main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ke sath tha. . . . iske baad unhon-ne ibne- Halhala ki riwayat ke ham mana hadis bayan ki hai aur is mein ye izafa hai ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they aur ye ke unhon-ne (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ""Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko Namaz padhai"" ke bajaey ""Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi"" kaha."
802,"abu-Kamil Fuzail-bin-Husain Jahdari ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne Usman bin-Abdullah-bin Mohab se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Jafar bin abi Sor se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kya main bakri ke gosht se wuzu karun? aap ne farmaya : chaho to wuzu kar lo aur chaho to na karo. usne kaha : oont ke gosht se wuzu karun? aap ne farmaya : haan, oont ke gosht se wuzu karo. usne kaha : kya bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz padh loon ? aap ne farmaya : haan. usne kaha : oonton ke bithaney ki jagah mein Namaz padh lun? aap ne farmaya : nahi."
803,"Samak, Usman bin-Abdullah-bin Mohab aur Ashas bin abi Shasa sab ne Jafar bin abi Sor se, unhon-ne Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah abu-Awana se abu-Kamil ne riwayat ki."
804,"Amr Naqid , Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed (bin Musaiyab (aur Ibad bin Tameem se aur unhon-ne un ( Ibad (ke chacha se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aadmi ke hawale se shikayat ki gaee ke usey ye khayal aata rehta hai ke wo Namaz ke doran mein koi cheez mehsus karta hai. aap ne farmaya : (wo Namaz se) na hatey yahan tak ke koi awaz suney ya koi bo mehsus kare. Abu-Bakar aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne apni riwayat main (Ibad bin Tameem ke chacha ke barey mein) bataya ke wo Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
805,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko apne pet mein kuchh mehsus ho aur usey shuba ho jaey ke usmein se kuchh nikla hai ya nahi to hargiz masjid se na nikley yahan tak ke awaz suney ya bo mehsus kar ley."
806,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur ibne-abi-Umar sab ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se, unhon-ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki aazad karda londi ko sadqey mein bakri di gaee, wo mar gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas se guzrey to aap ne farmaya : tum ne iska chamda kyon na utara , usko rang letey aur us se fayda utha letey ! logon ne bataya : ye murdar hai. aap ne farmaya : bas iska khana haram hai. Abu-Bakar aur ibne-abi-Umar ne apni riwayat main (an-Ibne-Abbas, an-Memuna) kaha (sanad mein riwayat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aagey Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf mansub ki.)"
807,"ibne-Shahab Zohri ke doosrey shagird Yunus ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik murdar bakri ( padi ( paai jo Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki londi ko sadqey mein di gaee thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne iske chamdey se fayda kyon na uthaya!'' logon ne kaha : ye murdar hai. aap ne farmaya : '' bas iska khana haram hai.''"
808,ibne-Shahab ke aik aur shagird Saleh ne bhi isi sanad se Yunus ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
809,"Sufiyan ne Amr se, unhon-ne Ata se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik murda padi hui bakri ke paas se guzrey jo Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki baandi ko bataur sadqa di gaee thi to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne iske chamdey ko kyon na utara, wo usko rang letey aur fayda utha letey !"
810,"ibne-Juraij ne Amr-bin-Dinar se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke aik bakri, jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik biwi ki thi, mar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne iska chamda utaar kar us se fayda kyon nahi uthaya !"
811,Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman ne Ata ke hawale se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki baandi ki) murda ( bakri ke paas se guzrey to aap ne farmaya : tum ne iske chamdey se fayda kyon na uthaya!
812,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Wala se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se khabar di, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : jab chamdey ko rang liya jata hai to wo paak ho jata hai."
813,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad aur Sufiyan Sory ne mukhtalif sanadon ke sath Zaid-bin-Aslam ki pichhli sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki, yani Yahya-bin-Yahya ki hadis ki tarah ."
814,"Yazeed bin abi Habib ne abu-Khair se riwayat ki ke maine Ali-bin-Wala Sabai ko aik posteen ( chamdey ka koot ( pahney huey dekha, maine usey chhuwa to usne kaha : usey kyon chhotey ho? maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha : ham maghrib mein hotey hain aur hamarey sath bar bar aur majoosi hotey hain, hamarey paas mendha laya jata hai jisey unhon-ne zabah kya hota hai aur ham unke zabah kiye huey janwar nahi khaatey, wo hamarey paas mishkeeza latey hain jis mein wo charbi daltey hain. to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha tha. aap ne farmaya : usko rangna usko paak kar deta hai."
815,"Jafar bin Rabeea ne abu-Khair se riwayat ki, kaha : mujh se ibne- Wala Sabai ne bayan kya ke maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : ham maghrib mein hotey hain to majusi hamarey paas pani aur charbi ke mishkeezey latey hain. unhon-ne kaha : pi liya karo. maine puchha : kya aap apni raey bata rahe hain? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : usko rangna usko paak kar deta hai."
816,"Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim (bin Muhammad ( ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik safar mein aap ke sath nikley, jab ham beda ya zaat-al-Jaish ke maqam par pahunchey to mera haar toot kar gir gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski talash ki khaatir thahar gaey, sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath ruk gaey, na wo pani ( wali jagah ( par they na unke paas pani ( bacha hua) tha. log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha : kya aapko pata nahi, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sath (doosrey ( logon ko rok rakha hai, na wo pani (wali jagah) par hain aur na logon ke paas pani bacha hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey (is waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri raan par sar rakh kar so chukey they aur kaha : tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aur aap ke sathiyon ko rok rakha hai jabke na wo pani wali jagah par hain aur na unke paas pani hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey daanta aur jo kuchh Allah ko manzoor tha kaha aur apne hath se meri kokh mein kachokey lagaaney lagey, mujhey sirf is baat ne harkat karne se rokey rakha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar meri raan par tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) soey rahe aur pani ke baghair hi subah hogi. is par Allah Taala ne tayammum ki aayat utari to sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhum) ne tayammum kya. Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jo nuqba mein se they, kaha : aey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke khandan ! ye aap ki pehli barkat nahi hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ham ne us oont ko jis par main sawar thi uthaya to hamein iske nichey se haar mil gaya."
817,"Hisham ke walid Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se aariyatan haar liya, wo gum ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne kuchh sathiyon ko uski talash ke liye bhejaa. unki Namaz ka waqt aa gaya to unhon-ne baghair wuzu ke Namaz padh li aur jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap se is baat ki shikayat ki, (us par) tayammum ki aayat utri to Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se) kaha : Allah aapko behtreen jazaa de, Allah ki qism ! aapko kabhi koi mushkil mamla pesh nahi aaya magar Allah Taala ne aap ke liye us se nikalney ki sabeel paida kar di aur usi mein musalmanon ke liye barkat rakh kar di."
818,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha. Hazrat abu-Musa ne puchha : abu Abdur-Rehman ! bataiye agar insan haalate-janabat mein ho aur aik maah tak usey pani na miley to wo Namaz ka kya karey? is par Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne jawab diya : wo tayammum na karey, chahey usey aik maah tak pani na miley. is par abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to sura Mayda ki us aayat ka kya matlab hai : tum pani na paogey to paak mitti se tayammum karo ? is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : agar unhein us aayat ki bina par rukhsat de di gaee to khatrah hai jab unhein pani thanda mehsus hoga to wo mitti se tayammum kar lengey. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya aap ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye baat nahi suni ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi kaam ke liye bheja , mujhey janabat ho gaee aur pani na mila to main chaupaaey ki tarah mitti mein lot-pot hua (aur Namaz padh li ( , phir main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap se iska tazkira kya to aap ne farmaya : tumharey liye bas apne donon hathon se is tarah karna kafi tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath aik baar zamin par maarey , phir baain hath ko daain par aur apni donon hatheliyon ki pusht par aur apne chehrey par mala. to Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne jawab diya : kya tumhen malum nahi ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Ammar Mina (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat par mut'ma'in nahi huey they. ( tafseel aagey hadis : 820 mein hai.)"
819,"abdul-Wahid ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki, kaha : abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha. . . phir abu-Muawiya ki (pichhli ( hadis poorey waqiey samet bayan ki, magar ye ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye is tarah kar lena hi kafi tha. aur apne donon hath zamin par maarey , ( phir ( apne donon hath jhaadey aur apne chehrey aur hatheliyon par masah kya."
820,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujh se Hakam ne zar ( bin-Abdullah-bin Zarara ( se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur puchha : main junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ho gaya hon aur mujhey pani nahi mila. to unhon-ne jawab diya : Namaz na padh . is par Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ameerul-momenin ! kya aapko yad nahi, jab main aur aap aik fauji dastey mein they, to ham junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ho gaey aur pani na mila to aap ne Namaz na padhi aur main mitti mein lot-pot ho gaya aur Namaz padh li to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye bas itna hi kafi tha ke apne donon hath zamin par maartey , phir unmein phoonk mar kar un donon se apne chehrey aur apni hatheliyon ka masah kar letey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Ammar ! Allah se daro. ( Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) jawab diya : agar aap chahtey hain to main ye waqia bayan nahi karta. Hakam ne kaha : yahi riwayat mujhey ( zar ke waastey ke baghair ( ibne- Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza ne apne walid se seedhey-seedhey bhi sunai jo jyon ka tyon zar ki hadis ki tarah thi. kaha : mujhey Salma ne zar ke hawale se hukm ki bayan ki hui sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ne jis cheez (ki zimme-dari ( ko utha liya hai ham usey aap hi par daltey hain (aap apne aitimad par ye riwayat bayan kar saktey hain.)"
821,"Nazar-bin-Shumail ne Shoba se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur puchha : main junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ho gaya hon aur mujhey pani nahi mila. iske baad) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya ke Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey ameerul-momenin ! agar aap chaahein to aap ke us haq ki bina par jo Allah Taala ne mujh par rakha hai, main ye hadis kisi ko na sunaunga aur) Shoba ne yahan ( mujhey Salma ne zar se hadis bayan ki (ke alfaz (ka zikr nahi kya."
822,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Umer bayan kartey hain ke main aur Abdur-Rehman bin Yasar , jo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam they, abu-jaham bin-Haaris bin Simma Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunchey to abu-jaham (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) biar jamal ( naam ke jagah ( se tashrif laey to aapko aik aadmi mila, us ne aapko salam kaha to aap ne iske salam ka jawab na diya yahan tak ke aap aik diwar ki taraf badhey aur aap ne apne chehrey aur hathon par masah kya, phir iske salam ka jawab diya."
823,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, aik aadmi guzra jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peshab kar rahe they, to usne salam kaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey salam ka jawab na diya."
824,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo janabat ki haalat mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke raston mein se kisi rastey par unhein miley to wo khisak gaey aur ja kar ghusl kya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein talash karwaya . jab wo aap ki khidmat mein aaey to aap ne farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! tum kahan they? , unhon-ne kaha ! aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! jab aap mujhey miley to main janabat ki haalat mein tha, maine ghusl kiye baghair aap ke paas baithna pasand na kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! momin napak ( napak ( nahi hota. (yani is tarah napak nahi hota ke usey koi chhu jaey, qareeb baithey ya us se hath milaaey to wo bhi napak ho jaey. ("
825,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein miley jabke wo junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) they, to wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se door hat gaey aur ghusl kya, phir aa kar kaha ke main junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman napak nahi hota."
826,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne tamam waqton mein Allah Taala ka zikr kartey they."
827,"Hammad ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Huweris se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( hath dho kar) baitul-khala se nikley to aap ke samney khana pesh kya gaya, logon ne aap se wuzu ka tazkira kya to aap ne farmaya : (kya ( mein Namaz padhna chahta hun ke wuzu karun?"
828,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kehtey they ke ham Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas they ke aap qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki jagah se ( hath dho kar) aaey to aap ke samney khana pesh kya gaya, aap se puchha gaya : kya aap wuzu nahi farmaaengey ? aap ne jawab diya : kis liye? kya mujhey Namaz padhni hai ke wuzu karun?"
829,"Muhammad-bin Muslim Taaifi ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne aal Saaib ke aazad karda ghulam Saeed bin Huweris se riwayat ki ke usne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko (ye ( kehtey huey suna : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye tashrif le gaey, jab aap aaey to aapko khana pesh kya gaya, aap se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool! kya aap wuzu nahi farmaengey ? aap ne jawab diya : kis liye? kya Namaz ke liye?"
830,"ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai ke hamein Saeed bin Huweris ne hadis bayan ki, us ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( door) bahar apni qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) kar li to khana aap ke qareeb laya gaya, aap ne tanawul farma liya aur pani ko na chhuwa . (aap pani sath ley jatey they. ( (ibne-Juraij (ka qaul hai : Amr-bin-Dinar ne mujhey Saeed bin Huweris se ye cheez zayed batai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : aap ne wuzu nahi kiya? aap ne jawab diya : maine Namaz padhney ka irada nahi kya ke wuzu karun. Amr ne kaha hai ke usne Saeed bin Huweris se suna hai."
831,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Hushaim se, un donon ne Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki) Hammad ki hadis mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab baitul-khala mein dakhil hotey aur Hushaim ke alfaz hain : jab kisi ot wali jagah mein dakhil hotey ( to farmatey : aey Allah ! main nar aur mada (male+female) donon qism ki khabees makhlooq se teri panah mein aata hun."
832,Ismail bin-Ulaih ne usi uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath Abdul-Azeez se riwayat bayan ki aur) dua ke) ye alfaz bayan kiye : ( أعوذ بالله من الخبث والخبائث) main nar aur mada (male+female) donon qism ki khabees makhlooq se Allah ki panah mein aata hun.
833,"Ismail bin-Ulaih aur Abdul Waris donon ne Abdul-Azeez se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Namaz ke liye takbeer keh di gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik aadmi se bahut qareeb ho kar ahista-ahista baat kar rahe they. ( Abdul Waris ki riwayat main (ورسول الله Mina نجي لرجل) ke bajaey ( ونبی الله ﷺ یناجی الرجل ) aap aik aadmi se ahista-ahista baatein kar rahe they hai. mafhoom aik hai) to aap Namaz ke liye khadey nahi huey yahan tak ke log ( baithey baithey ( so gaey."
834,"Shoba ne Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Namaz ke liye takbeer keh di gaee jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik aadmi se sargoshi farma rahe they. aap us se sargoshi farmatey rahe yahan tak ke aap ke sathi ( baithey baithey ( so gaey, iske baad aap aaey aur unhein Namaz padhai."
835,"Shoba ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : maine saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ( baithey baithey ( so jatey they, phir wuzu kiye baghair Namaz padh letey. ( Shoba kehtey hain : ( maine ( Qatada se) puchha : aap ne ye hadis Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan ! Allah ki qism !"
836,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : isha ki Namaz ke liye iqamat keh di gaee to aik aadmi ne ( Rasulullah se) kaha : mera aik kaam hai, chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar us se sargoshi karne lagey yahan tak ke log ya kuchh log ( baithey baithey ( so gaey, phir sab ne Namaz padhi."
